snippet.title: Fearmonium - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1068360/Fearmonium/

Fearmonium is a psychedelic metroidvania where suspense intertwines with humor. Start the game as the usual unpleasant memory and reincarnate into a real phobia by breaking through the most hidden corners of consciousness of Max.

Voicing: Ty Harper
Music: Expecte Amour - https://expecteamour.bandcamp.com/
Press-kit:  https://redblackspade.com
